'''三氟化錳'''（[[化學式|化學式]]：[[锰|Mn]][[氟|F]]<sub>3</sub>）是一种固体，可以用[[二氟化錳|二氟化錳]]和[[氟气|氟气]]合成。这种红色略带紫色的固体用作有机化合物（例如[[烃|烃]]类）的[[氟化剂|氟化剂]]。<ref>Burley, G. A.; Taylor, R. "Manganese(III) fluoride" in Encyclopedia of Reagents for Organic Synthesis (Ed: L. Paquette) 2004, J. Wiley & Sons, New York. {{DOI|10.1002/047084289}}</ref>它也会形成一种水合物。

==合成，结构与反应==
===合成===
三氟化錳可以在[[氟化氢|氟化氢]]溶液中用[[二氟化錳|二氟化錳]]和[[氟气|氟气]]合成：<ref name="mad">{{cite journal
| title = Room temperature syntheses of MnF<sub>3</sub>, MnF<sub>4</sub> and hexafluoromanganete(IV) salts of alkali cations
| author = Z. Mazej
| journal = Journal of Fluorine Chemistry
| year = 2002
| volume = 114
| issue = 1
| pages = 75–80
| doi = 10.1016/S0022-1139(01)00566-8
}}</ref>

:MnF<sub>2</sub>+0.5F<sub>2</sub>→MnF<sub>3</sub>
也可以在高温250℃用卤化锰和[[氟|氟]]之间的反应合成。<ref name="shap">Inorganic chemistry, Catherine E. Housecroft, A.G. Sharpe, pp.711-712, section ''Manganese (III)'' , [http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=3sy4ZAP4EGAC&dq googlebooks link] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=3sy4ZAP4EGAC&dq |date=20121112041108 }}</ref>
===结构===
在结晶状态下，三氟化錳类似[[三氟化钒|三氟化钒]]：具有相同M-F分子键长的八面体金属中心。然而，在锰化合物中Mn-F键（距离为1.79﹑1.91﹑2.09Å）因[[姜-泰勒效应|姜-泰勒效应]]而被扭曲。（也因此单元电池的[[单斜晶系|单斜晶系]]对抗更高的对称性）<ref>Wells, A.F. (1984) Structural Inorganic Chemistry, Oxford: Clarendon Press. ISBN 0-19-855370-6.</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author = Hepworth, M. A.; Jack, K. H.; [[Ronald_Sydney_Nyholm|Nyholm]], R. S. | title = Interatomic Bonding in Manganese Trifluoride | journal = [[Nature_(journal)|Nature]] | year = 1957 | volume = 179 | pages = 211–212 | doi = 10.1038/179211b0 | issue = 4552}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal
| title = The crystal structure of manganese trifluoride, MnF<sub>3</sub>
| author = M. A. Hepworth, K. H. Jack
| journal = Acta Crystallographica
| year = 1957
| volume = 10
| issue =5
| pages = 345–351
| doi = 10.1107/S0365110X57001024}}
</ref>

水合物MnF<sub>3</sub>·3H<sub>2</sub>O可以通过结晶作用，把MnF<sub>3</sub>溶在[[氢氟酸|氢氟酸]]中得到。这个水合物不寻常，因为它形成了两个不同的结构（[Mn(H<sub>2</sub>O)<sub>4</sub>F<sub>2</sub>]<sup>+</sup>与[Mn(H<sub>2</sub>O)<sub>2</sub>F<sub>4</sub>]<sup>-</sup>）且有[[空间群|空间群]]P2<sub>1</sub>/c和P2<sub>1</sub>/a。<ref>Structures of two polymorphs of MnF3·3H2O , Michel Molinier and Werner Massa , Journal of Fluorine Chemistry , Volume 57, Issues 1-3, April–June 1992, pp.139-146 , [http://www.sciencedirect.com/science?_ob=ArticleURL&_udi=B6TGD-42H1S9S-21&_user=10&_coverDate=06/30/1992&_rdoc=1&_fmt=high&_orig=search&_sort=d&_docanchor=&view=c&_searchStrId=1370631000&_rerunOrigin=google&_acct=C000050221&_version=1&_urlVersion=0&_userid=10&md5=aadd1956f6c1e3401bf08c1e14c2ee88 online abstract via ''www.sciencedirect.com''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science?_ob=ArticleURL&_udi=B6TGD-42H1S9S-21&_user=10&_coverDate=06%2F30%2F1992&_rdoc=1&_fmt=high&_orig=search&_sort=d&_docanchor=&view=c&_searchStrId=1370631000&_rerunOrigin=google&_acct=C000050221&_version=1&_urlVersion=0&_userid=10&md5=aadd1956f6c1e3401bf08c1e14c2ee88 |date=20190218223614 }}</ref>

===反应===
三氟化錳与[[氟化钠|氟化钠]]反应得出八面体六氟砷酸钾阴离子：<ref name="shap"/>
:3NaF + MnF<sub>3</sub> → Na<sub>3</sub>MnF<sub>6</sub>
其他反应条件给出化合物MnF<sub>5</sub><sup>2-</sup>或MnF<sub>4</sub><sup>-</sup>阴离子。这些阴离子分别是链和层结构，并桥接氟。锰在这些物质中保持6坐标﹑八面体和三价。<ref name="shap"/>
 
三氟化錳可以氟化有机化合物，包括芳烃<ref>[http://notes.fluorine1.ru/contents/Nov98/Notes/letters/letter1.html Fluorination of p-chlorobenzotrifluoride by manganese trifluoride] {{Wayback|url=http://notes.fluorine1.ru/contents/Nov98/Notes/letters/letter1.html |date=20110823102228 }} A. Kachanov, V. Kornilov, V.Belogay , Fluorine Notes :Vol. 1 (1) November–December 1998 , via ''notes.fluorine1.ru''</ref>﹑环丁烯<ref>Fluorination of fluoro-cyclobutene with high-valency metal fluoride m Junji Mizukado, Yasuhisa Matsukawa, Heng-dao Quan, Masanori Tamura, Akira Sekiya , Journal of Fluorine Chemistry
Volume 127, Issue 1, January 2006, Pages 79-84 , [http://www.sciencedirect.com/science?_ob=ArticleURL&_udi=B6TGD-4HNS6P9-2&_user=10&_coverDate=01/31/2006&_rdoc=1&_fmt=high&_orig=search&_sort=d&_docanchor=&view=c&_acct=C000050221&_version=1&_urlVersion=0&_userid=10&md5=1be7e0e886c36ce120b73ca1d2e37710 online abstract via ''www.sciencedirect.com''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science?_ob=ArticleURL&_udi=B6TGD-4HNS6P9-2&_user=10&_coverDate=01%2F31%2F2006&_rdoc=1&_fmt=high&_orig=search&_sort=d&_docanchor=&view=c&_acct=C000050221&_version=1&_urlVersion=0&_userid=10&md5=1be7e0e886c36ce120b73ca1d2e37710 |date=20190218223614 }}</ref>和富勒烯。<ref>Fluorination of the cubic and hexagonal C60 modifications by crystalline manganese trifluoride , Physics of the Solid State , Volume 44, Number 4 , 4/2002 , pp.629-630 , V.É. Aleshina, A.Ya. Borshchevskii, E.V. Skokan, I.V. Arkhangel’skii, A.V. Astakhov, N.B. Shustova , [http://www.springerlink.com/content/g563v8hl256uh2l5/ online abstract via ''www.springerlink''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.springerlink.com/content/g563v8hl256uh2l5/ |date=20200305193040 }}</ref>
 
三氟化錳加热后分解为[[氟化锰|氟化锰]]。<ref>[http://www.1911encyclopedia.org/Manganese Manganese; section ''Manganic Salts'' ] {{Wayback|url=http://www.1911encyclopedia.org/Manganese |date=20090130090426 }} via ''www.1911encyclopedia.org''</ref><ref>In situ time-resolved X-ray diffraction study of manganese trifluoride thermal decomposition , J.V. Raua, V. Rossi Albertinib, N.S. Chilingarova, S. Colonnab, U. Anselmi Tamburini, Journal of Fluorine Chemistry 4506 (2001) 1–4 , [http://ftp.esrf.eu/pub/UserReports/21876_A.pdf online version] {{Wayback|url=http://ftp.esrf.eu/pub/UserReports/21876_A.pdf |date=20171230114548 }}</ref>

==相关Mn<sup>3+</sup>化合物==
其他Mn<sup>3+</sup>化合物包括醋酸锰（CAS＃993-02-2），[[乙酰丙酮锰|乙酰丙酮锰]]（CAS＃14284-89-0），两者在[[有机合成|有机合成]]中都用作氧化剂。三氟化錳为路易斯酸性并会形成了各种不同的衍生物。其中有K<sub>2</sub>MnF<sub>3</sub>(SO<sub>4</sub>)<ref>{{cite journal | author = Bhattacharjee, M. N; Chaudhuri, M. K. | title = Dipotassium Trifluorosulfatomanganate(III) | journal = [[Inorg._Synth.|Inorg. Synth.]] | year = 1990 | volume = 27 | pages = 312–313 | doi = 10.1002/9780470132586.ch61}}</ref>和K<sub>2</sub>MnF<sub>5</sub>.

==安全注意事项==
跟其他活跃的无机氟化物一样，三氟化錳应存储在聚乙烯瓶，被皮肤接触或放在任何潮湿地区时会因水解而形成[[氢氟酸|氢氟酸]]。

